<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Thu, 16 Dec 2021 11:38:45 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>泰國廟推加密貨幣：崇笛幣，由龍婆匹開光+方便善信捐獻</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/16/somdejcoin/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=somdejcoin</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 16 Dec 2021 11:38:28 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[加密貨幣]]></category><category><![CDATA[崇笛]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1076472</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>近日泰國廟宇新推出加密貨幣 &#8211; 崇笛幣（Somdejcoin）SDC，並經由泰國僧人，龍婆匹（Lu [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>近日泰國廟宇新推出加密貨幣 &#8211; 崇笛幣（Somdejcoin）SDC，並經由泰國僧人，龍婆匹（Luang Por Pat Punyakamo）開光，限量 66,186,727 枚，與 2020 年泰國人口相約。官方指崇笛能為買家帶來好運外，亦可用作捐獻鮮花、貢品及香油錢。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/266463461_618176836195974_8862400502525397123_n.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1076485" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/266463461_618176836195974_8862400502525397123_n-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/266463461_618176836195974_8862400502525397123_n-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/266463461_618176836195974_8862400502525397123_n-675x900.jpg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/266463461_618176836195974_8862400502525397123_n-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/266463461_618176836195974_8862400502525397123_n.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></a></p><p>崇笛將在本月 24 日 05:00 UTC 起，可於加密貨幣交易網站 Hotbit 交易所上存款，亦於同日 07:00 UTC 起接受交易，以穩定幣 USDT 或比特幣交易。不過系統會於每次交易時自動扣除 9% 費用，作支援佛教發展、加強貨幣流動性、及增加持幣者持幣量之用。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/266460408_2713104482325477_9005041336090457539_n-546x1024-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1076497" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/266460408_2713104482325477_9005041336090457539_n-546x1024-1-309x580.jpg" alt="" width="309" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/266460408_2713104482325477_9005041336090457539_n-546x1024-1-309x580.jpg 309w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/266460408_2713104482325477_9005041336090457539_n-546x1024-1-480x900.jpg 480w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/266460408_2713104482325477_9005041336090457539_n-546x1024-1.jpg 546w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 309px" /></a></p><p>美國證券交易委員會質疑崇笛是否符合數位交易所的上市規則，根據上市規則有關貨幣不能為 Memes 幣（meme tokens）、粉絲幣 （fan tokens）、非同質化代幣（non-fungible tokens）及交易所發行的數碼代幣。委員會又指崇笛未有明確交待貨幣及交易等細節，提醒買家交易前應謹慎了解貨幣資料。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.siambitcoin.com/2021/12/14/somdej-sdc-2/">Siambitcoin.com</a>, <a href="https://www.bangkokpost.com/business/2217267/sec-issues-warning-over-thai-temples-coin">Bangkok Post</a></p><p>—</p><p><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
